pid":"d5840635865836424bba78980f3da2c8ff89b240","tid":1020660,"uid":693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ad8538115a0d307370f6377a032250ab0f542e4e","tid":1020660,"uid":154594,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"58ec30c98066267d43e493dbe0a4b1f4a6b5cfaa","tid":1020660,"uid":223098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T05:55:55.000Z","msg":"成程trip大嘅洗咗幾多錢 THX"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T06:39:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FMpwLm1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFMpwLm1.png&h=f867e5ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n成個trip11日9夜消費如下，不過舊嗰張信用卡都有一d數係呢個trip 所以你當total 20000-21000"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T07:18:18.000Z","msg":"冇住宿費既?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T07:23:01.000Z","msg":"用現金或信用卡俾，不過有一晚酒店之前俾左冇計入去，780蚊左右"},{"pid":"e074793b316fd8b548f6ee1b75c6c8e2baa83a5c","tid":1020660,"uid":154594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bb0da9a858b1535891991a3006a20a3896953a3f","tid":1020660,"uid":10901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T05:29:22.000Z","msg":"幾點天黑？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T07:23:19.000Z","msg":"五點"},{"pid":"0ace7ccbfc52126b84aea65421a93bd5d292c95d","tid":1020660,"uid":10901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e074793b316fd8b548f6ee1b75c6c8e2baa83a5c","tid":1020660,"uid":154594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bb0da9a858b1535891991a3006a20a3896953a3f","tid":1020660,"uid":10901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T05:29:22.000Z","msg":"幾點天黑？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T07:23:19.000Z","msg":"五點"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T11:54:23.000Z","msg":"Ok喎<br />\n係機票貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d5d1da7dfe2396083e1a38ae594685ad8953553","tid":1020660,"uid":154594,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T15:31:38.000Z","msg":"其實第五日唔係搭車就係揸車，都唔知講咩野好，不過都試下講下啦<br />\n<br />\n今日由Galway 出發到北愛城市Derry ，Bus Eireann 64號巴士，需時5個多小時，本來我早上四點多起身（訓唔著）可以趕及早上六點出發的巴士11點幾到，但由於hostel reception 未開未能checkout 所以依原定計劃坐8:45那一班<br />\n<br />\n原本我在背包客棧問行程時版友係建議我在都柏林機場先去Galway ，然後回都柏林，再上Belfast 及Derry會快一點，但是我因爲要在Belfast 坐船走而又唔想咁多回頭路所以保留自己嘅設計<br />\n<br />\n在hostel 邊食早餐邊同hostel 靚女volunteer 吹水完之後就上車，車資24euro，沿途時晴時雨，所以有以下呢幅<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NsT2ipa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNsT2ipa.png&h=2b54d119&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大約坐了個多小時發生了一件怪事，有個女仔上車不停問人借電話打俾阿媽，話之前留低自己成袋行李係另一架車喎，點知佢想帶埋借黎嘅電話衝落車，嚇死借電話嗰個要即刻收返個電話，都唔知個女仔想點嘅<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aNxq0E6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaNxq0E6.png&h=dc24ab31&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aqqgnTs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaqqgnTs.png&h=5adc8b72&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n由於車上冇廁所，所以如果你有興趣坐呢條線，你要把握佢係Sligo 停15分鐘換司機的機會去<br />\n<br />\n坐到14:30終於去到Derry，把握機會食個雞堡餐當午飯先，由於黎到英國領土下，轉用英鎊，我買完野找錢時收到一堆50便士，感覺似曾相識（係呢，後面個事頭婆嘜頭<br />\n），於是幫佢影左張相<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mLYBnWb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmLYBnWb.png&h=501614ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後返去Foyle Street巴士總站上147號巴士入機場取車，由於這次是我第一次一個人駕駛所以好緊張，而由於係租棍波關係，我在香港又未算練得熟，所以緊張關頭一波起步時會死火，後面就會嗶你。之後又試過行錯路，第一次係錯過左可以快D到目的地的天橋，攪到要入市中心再搵路走，第二次係錯過左入酒店的路口，要在下個路口找小路掉頭，但掉頭時又蝦碌架車剷左上泥到。好彩架車到達酒店時係下圖嘅樣<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tuoRbSA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtuoRbSA.png&h=7dd5b31e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bdMvsqW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbdMvsqW.png&h=96c47af6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f5zdqcC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff5zdqcC.png&h=b36d3c83&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我本來想夜晚出去睇星，不過見天氣唔算好，就改為第二朝先去玩，夜晚晚餐食左個Fillet with Chips（酒店內），酒店Ok 但有少少破舊"},{"pid":"28e743d626cb69f177f1e2ad1624aca1c2f53df3","tid":1020660,"uid":38376,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T12:03:23.000Z","msg":"如果佢問China我會寧願答佢Taiwan。<br />\n因為佢哋起碼知道Taiwan係一個country"},{"pid":"bb32bd4be53b40c748b64359e99e0a1021ac3224","tid":1020660,"uid":99816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T12:08:33.000Z","msg":"負皮係比支那人"},{"pid":"4139f12260571656a38a1c1cabe835c473d5cb8d","tid":1020660,"uid":34899,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"28e743d626cb69f177f1e2ad1624aca1c2f53df3","tid":1020660,"uid":38376,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T12:03:23.000Z","msg":"如果佢問China我會寧願答佢Taiwan。<br />\n因為佢哋起碼知道Taiwan係一個country"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T17:14:44.000Z","msg":"HONg KONG 就HONG KONG<br />\n佢唔識就解釋比佢聽<br />\n做咩要認自己做第個垃圾地方<br />\n認新加坡呀不如"}]}